{
  "stem": "10588.8",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I like him till this day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Thank God, he's alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But as a friend.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a brother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No otherwise.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one time, he makes-- made a party.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he invited Bina and I to come.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got very insulted, because I didn't know he inviting Bina too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you think I'm that kind of a girl?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm going to go to a boyfriend's apartment?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, shh, shh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm not inviting just you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm inviting Bina.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as soon as I came in, a man was sitting there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, I didn't know him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said in Polish to me, here is room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can sit down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from the minute I saw him, I liked him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And his name is Rachmil Zygmuntowicz, which is my husband now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was worried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we clicked it off just like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just like with Abram, I didn't have any emotional-- like contact, you know, like-- with Rachmil, immediately.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was worried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What about Bina?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we wouldn't separate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he had a friend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Rachmil was born in Belchatow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "His friend, Mendel [POLISH]-- may he rest in peace, he's no longer alive-- was also from Belchatow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Shmolevicz was also from Belchatow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Since he saw that I am not going to marry him, he brought Rachmil and Mendel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he later said, if you cannot be for-- for-- for me, let it be for my friend, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he gave me a little bit of [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It wasn't-- and we met.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I said to him, why don't you ask your friend to come too?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He's going to take me home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So he took Mendel too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then was a-- a funny little story.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
